high_descs: Go to the waste basket next to the fridge.
Take the apple from the waste basket.
Go to the fridge to your left.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Place the apple in the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the trash.

high_descs: Walk forward to the trash can.
Pick up the apple out of the trash can.
Go to the fridge on your left.
Put the apple in the fridge, then take it out again.
Turn to the right and go back to the trash can.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple from the fridge into the trash can.

high_descs: Go ahead to the white bin.
Take the apple out of the bin.
Go to the refrigerator to the left of the bin.
Put the apple in the refrigerator to the right of the lettuce. Close then open the refrigerator door. Take the apple.
Go to the white bin to the right of the refrigerator.
Put the apple in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in a bin.
